VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(url|re_path)\s*\(\s*['"](\^|\^\/)([^'"]+)['"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:login_required|permission_required|LoginRequired|csrf_protect
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects insecure URL configurations in Django's URL patterns.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure URL Configuration.
